title: Ilfenesh Hadera: Spike Lee Alum And DJ School Dropout
description: Ilfenesh Hadera, from She's Gotta Have It, chats about growing up in Harlem, working with Spike Lee, and her new series, Godfather Of Harlem. This episode originally aired September 13, 2019.
